head.note:
In English and Czechoslovak languages;
                        Czechoslovak text not printed. Ratification advised by the Senate, Jan. 26,
                        1929; ratified by the President, Feb. 14, 1929; ratified by Czechoslovakia,
                        Sept. 14, 1929; ratifications exchanged at Washington, Nov. 14, 1929;
                        proclaimed by the President, Nov. 14, 1929.
